data.description: Beautiful home renovated by current owners. 3 bed 2 bath home with office, a major kitchen remodeled with granite counters tops, appliances and engineered laminate flooring. A new Gas heater and A/C, also a covered deck in back. New vanities and granite counters in bathrooms. Lots of Storage in the garage. This vaulted andopen floor plan allows for large family gatherings. Recently appraised for $497,000.  Large RV shelteroff driveway for RV, Travel Trailer or Large Boat. Storage shed in back with a fully fenced backyard.This corner lot is close to shopping center, grocery stores, and easy access to Bend or Sisters.
